column1: # Totals for 1910 and 1911, before monthly readings began, have been omitted.
# The March 1933 figure is shown bracketed and has been adjusted from other sites, and has been omitted.
# The March 1936 total is shown bracketed and noted as inaccurate, although none of the monthly figures are bracketed. It has been retained.
# The Old House is now 27 Front Street.
# The station continued until 1961 according to MIDAS.
